metadata.name: Tourmaline
metadata.description:
Friendly beam. Amazing combination and color mixing are sharpened in an elegant form.

In ordinary conditions, the stone usually finds the owner by itself, becoming not only a companion, but also a faithful friend. 
Able to clean space and neutralize weak poisons. 

But more often due to its high healing properties, it is used by healers who in large quantities buy stones from prospectors or tradesmans


4000 x 4000, 1/1.
